subject: NCAA Baseball Championships
Baseball (College)
lead_paragraph: Matt Noble was 2 for 3 with three runs batted in, and Bethune-Cookman withstood a late Columbia rally to beat the Lions, 6-5, in an elimination game at the Coral Gables, Fla., N.C.A.A. regional.
